// used in a Chrome App build (i.e. by Brave Browser).
//
// Bug reports:
// - Chrome: https://bugs.chromium.org/p/chromium/issues/detail?id=734880
// - Firefox: https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1374505
